163
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,240
I will let you know

164
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,040
you will not regret

165
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,320
following me.

166
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,240
Your Highness, you want to...

167
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:19,640
I'll take back everything
that should belong to me.

168
